Class ViewChoice

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.awt.Component
      • java.awt.Choice
        • wt.clients.beans.ViewChoice
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.awt.image.ImageObserver, java.awt.ItemSelectable, java.awt.MenuContainer, java.io.Serializable, javax.accessibility.Accessible

    public class ViewChoice
extends java.awt.Choice
    This class allows the selection of a wt.vc.views.View in a choice list. The choice list is populated with a list of all the Views defined in the system.



    Supported API: true

    Extendable: false

    See Also:
    wt.vc.views.View;, Serialized Form
